{"tid":2389927,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"張偉文過馬路連人帶輪椅打觔斗 跌地受傷急召白車送院","createTime":"2021-02-01T08:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T09:43:08.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2a5637dcb65d52d1ba8bce84b05ca5c2f3c2264d","tid":2389927,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T08:30:28.000Z","msg":"現年63歲的「靚聲王」張偉文，近年受腰患、糖尿病及腳痛問題困擾，要坐輪椅及靠枴杖代步，今日有消息指張偉文在所住的護老院樓下跌倒，被白車送入醫院救治，《蘋果》致電張偉文問候，他說：「我而家喺白車，啱啱過馬路時連人帶輪椅打觔斗跌咗落地下。」<br />\n<br />\n電話中的張偉文聲如洪鐘報平安：「我推住輪椅嘅時候，因為輪椅行得唔順，所以人同輪椅一齊打觔斗，右邊背脊有少少酸痛，血都冇滴，唔使擔心，可能唔使留醫添。」問到有否嚇親？張偉文無奈說：「嚇親都冇辦法，冇乜事就算，自己打999報警，白車好快到。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210201/DBKF3GYZG5F23CTYJDVWIMQERM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210201%2FDBKF3GYZG5F23CTYJDVWIMQERM%2F&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G1IIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=d1397421\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210201%2FDBKF3GYZG5F23CTYJDVWIMQERM%2F&h=818ffeb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210201/DBKF3GYZG5F23CTYJDVWIMQERM/</a>"},{"pid":"0f2f7c64df8d2d537dbba99ade05c5fdf3c7bd26","tid":2389927,"uid":164500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T08:31:46.000Z","msg":"無人理佢"},{"pid":"7edeb71518f7520d3c85283fece2ce35cc49c88c","tid":2389927,"uid":282352,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T08:45:10.000Z","msg":"F1方程式霍金有接班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082bf2b12ea40ce2312fab38f15b125dbd307afc","tid":2389927,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T08:46:52.000Z","msg":"乜搞成咁啊？"},{"pid":"bcb40f0a2acc2f28926ed9ea72b3e11bdd723113","tid":2389927,"uid":104516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T08:47:01.000Z","msg":"而家瘦到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"